      </div>
    </div>
  </div>
</section>

<!-- ══ FAQ ══ -->
<section class="ds-faq">
  <div class="ds-faq-inner">
    <p class="ds-eyebrow" style="text-align:center">COMMON QUESTIONS</p>
    <h2 class="ds-section-title" style="text-align:center">Frequently Asked Questions</h2>
    <div class="ds-faq-list">
      <details class="ds-faq-item"><summary class="ds-faq-q"><span>🔥</span> Will this mat melt or warp from grill heat? <svg class="ds-chev" viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="2" width="16" height="16"><polyline points="6 9 12 15 18 9"/></svg></summary><p class="ds-faq-a">No. The mat is designed to be placed around the base of the grill, not directly under open flames. It handles radiant heat, hot embers, and UV rays without warping, cracking, or melting.</p></details>
      <details class="ds-faq-item"><summary class="ds-faq-q"><span>🌧️</span> Can I leave it outside in the rain? <svg class="ds-chev" viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="2" width="16" height="16"><polyline points="6 9 12 15 18 9"/></svg></summary><p class="ds-faq-a">Yes — it's 100% weather-resistant PVC. Rain, morning dew, and sun won't damage it. For storage, we recommend rolling it up and hanging it during extended off-season periods.</p></details>
      <details class="ds-faq-item"><summary class="ds-faq-q"><span>📐</span> Will it fit my grill? <svg class="ds-chev" viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="2" width="16" height="16"><polyline points="6 9 12 15 18 9"/></svg></summary><p class="ds-faq-a">At 65" × 36", it accommodates most standard gas grills, charcoal grills, smokers, and griddles. It provides ample coverage around all four sides of a typical grill setup.</p></details>
      <details class="ds-faq-item"><summary class="ds-faq-q"><span>🏠</span> Is it safe on wood decks? <svg class="ds-chev" viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="2" width="16" height="16"><polyline points="6 9 12 15 18 9"/></svg></summary><p class="ds-faq-a">Absolutely. It's specifically designed for wood, composite, and concrete surfaces. The non-slip backing won't scratch or damage your deck — it actually protects the surface from discoloration.</p></details>
      <details class="ds-faq-item"><summary class="ds-faq-q"><span>💧</span> How do I clean it? <svg class="ds-chev" viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="2" width="16" height="16"><polyline points="6 9 12 15 18 9"/></svg></summary><p class="ds-faq-a">Just rinse with a garden hose. For stubborn grease, use a mild dish soap and a soft brush. It dries quickly and is ready to use again within minutes.</p></details>
      <details class="ds-faq-item"><summary class="ds-faq-q"><span>↩️</span> What if I'm not happy with it? <svg class="ds-chev" viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="2" width="16" height="16"><polyline points="6 9 12 15 18 9"/></svg></summary><p class="ds-faq-a">We stand behind every mat with a 30-day money-back guarantee. If you're not satisfied for any reason, contact us and we'll issue a full refund — no hassle, no questions asked.</p></details>
    </div>
  </div>
</section>

<!-- ══ FOOTER ══ -->
<footer class="ds-footer">
  <div class="ds-footer-inner">
    <div>
      <p class="ds-footer-brand">{{ shop.name }}</p>
      <p class="ds-footer-tagline">Protect your deck. Enjoy your grill.</p>
    </div>
    <div class="ds-footer-links">
      <strong>Support</strong>
      <a href="/pages/contact">Contact Us</a>
      <a href="/pages/track-order">Track Order</a>
      <a href="/pages/faq">FAQ</a>
    </div>
    <div class="ds-footer-links">
      <strong>Policies</strong>
      <a href="/policies/privacy-policy">Privacy Policy</a>
      <a href="/policies/refund-policy">Refund Policy</a>
      <a href="/policies/terms-of-service">Terms of Service</a>
    </div>
  </div>
  <div class="ds-footer-bottom">
    <p>© {{ 'now' | date: '%Y' }} {{ shop.name }}. All rights reserved.</p>
    <div class="ds-footer-badges"><span>🔒 SSL Secured</span><span>✅ Verified Store</span><span>🛡️ Buyer Protected</span></div>
  </div>
</footer>

<!-- ══ STICKY BAR ══ -->
<div class="ds-sticky" id="ds-sticky">
  <div class="ds-sticky-info">
    <strong>{{ ds.title | truncate: 38 }}</strong>
    <span id="ds-sticky-price">{{ fv.price | money }}</span>
  </div>
  <button class="ds-sticky-cta" id="ds-sticky-btn">Add to Cart</button>
</div>

<script>
(function(){
  var variants = JSON.parse(document.getElementById('ds-variant-data').textContent);
  var mainImg  = document.getElementById('ds-main-img');
  var ctaBtn   = document.getElementById('ds-cta-btn');
  var stickyBtn= document.getElementById('ds-sticky-btn');
  var ctaPrice = document.getElementById('ds-cta-price');
  var priceEl  = document.getElementById('ds-price');
  var compareEl= document.getElementById('ds-compare');
  var stickyPr = document.getElementById('ds-sticky-price');
  var stickyBar= document.getElementById('ds-sticky');
  var v        = variants[0];

  function fmt(c){ return '$'+(c/100).toFixed(2); }

  function updateUI(){
    if(!v) return;
    if(ctaPrice)  ctaPrice.textContent  = fmt(v.price);
    if(priceEl)   priceEl.textContent   = fmt(v.price);
    if(stickyPr)  stickyPr.textContent  = fmt(v.price);
    if(compareEl){
      if(v.compare_at_price > v.price){ compareEl.textContent=fmt(v.compare_at_price); compareEl.style.display='inline'; }
      else { compareEl.style.display='none'; }
    }
  }

  // Thumbnails
  document.querySelectorAll('.ds-thumb').forEach(function(t){
    t.addEventListener('click', function(){
      if(mainImg) mainImg.src = t.dataset.src;
      document.querySelectorAll('.ds-thumb').forEach(function(x){ x.classList.remove('ds-thumb--active'); });
      t.classList.add('ds-thumb--active');
    });
  });

  // Add to cart
  async function addToCart(){
    var origHTML = ctaBtn ? ctaBtn.innerHTML : '';
    if(ctaBtn){ ctaBtn.disabled=true; ctaBtn.textContent='Adding…'; }
    if(stickyBtn){ stickyBtn.disabled=true; stickyBtn.textContent='Adding…'; }
    try {
      if(!v) throw new Error('no variant');
      var res = await fetch('/cart/add.js',{method:'POST',headers:{'Content-Type':'application/json','Accept':'application/json'},body:JSON.stringify({items:[{id:v.id,quantity:1}]})});
      if(!res.ok){ var e=await res.json().catch(function(){return{};}); throw new Error(e.description||'Cart error'); }
      // Update cart badge
      var cartRes = await fetch('/cart.js');
      var cart    = await cartRes.json();
      var badge   = document.querySelector('.ds-cart-badge');
      if(badge) badge.textContent = cart.item_count;
      if(ctaBtn){ ctaBtn.disabled=false; ctaBtn.innerHTML='✓ Added to Cart!'; setTimeout(function(){ ctaBtn.innerHTML=origHTML; },2000); }
      if(stickyBtn){ stickyBtn.disabled=false; stickyBtn.textContent='✓ Added!'; setTimeout(function(){ stickyBtn.textContent='Add to Cart'; },2000); }
      // Open drawer
      document.querySelector('.ds-open-cart') && document.querySelector('.ds-open-cart').click();
    } catch(err){
      alert('Could not add to cart: '+err.message);
      if(ctaBtn){ ctaBtn.disabled=false; ctaBtn.innerHTML=origHTML; }
      if(stickyBtn){ stickyBtn.disabled=false; stickyBtn.textContent='Add to Cart'; }
    }
  }

  if(ctaBtn)    ctaBtn.addEventListener('click', addToCart);
  if(stickyBtn) stickyBtn.addEventListener('click', addToCart);

  // Sticky bar
  var heroForm = document.querySelector('.ds-form');
  if(heroForm && stickyBar){
    var obs=new IntersectionObserver(function(e){ stickyBar.style.transform=e[0].isIntersecting?'translateY(100%)':'translateY(0)'; },{threshold:0.1});
    obs.observe(heroForm);
  }

  // Countdown
  var timerEl=document.getElementById('ds-timer');
  if(timerEl){
    var secs=11*3600+47*60+2;
    setInterval(function(){
      secs=Math.max(0,secs-1);
      var h=Math.floor(secs/3600),m=Math.floor((secs%3600)/60),s=secs%60;
      timerEl.textContent=[h,m,s].map(function(n){return n.toString().padStart(2,'0');}).join(':');
    },1000);
  }

  updateUI();
})();
</script>

<style>
/* ── Hero ── */
.ds-hero{background:#f8f8f6;padding:40px 20px 56px}
.ds-hero-layout{max-width:1080px;margin:0 auto;display:grid;grid-template-columns:1fr;gap:40px}
@media(min-width:780px){.ds-hero-layout{grid-template-columns:1.1fr 1fr;align-items:start;gap:56px}}

/* ── Gallery ── */
.ds-gallery-main{position:relative;border-radius:16px;overflow:hidden;background:#fff;box-shadow:0 4px 24px rgba(0,0,0,0.08);margin-bottom:12px}
.ds-main-img{width:100%;aspect-ratio:1/1;object-fit:cover;display:block}
.ds-award-badge{position:absolute;top:14px;left:14px;background:#e85d04;color:#fff;font-size:0.68rem;font-weight:800;padding:6px 14px;border-radius:99px;letter-spacing:0.06em}
.ds-thumbs{display:flex;gap:8px;flex-wrap:wrap}
.ds-thumb{width:72px;height:72px;border-radius:10px;overflow:hidden;border:2px solid transparent;background:#fff;cursor:pointer;box-shadow:0 2px 8px rgba(0,0,0,0.06);padding:0;transition:border-color 0.15s}
.ds-thumb img{width:100%;height:100%;object-fit:cover}
.ds-thumb--active{border-color:#e85d04;box-shadow:0 2px 8px rgba(232,93,4,0.25)}
.ds-thumb:hover{border-color:#e85d04}

/* ── Form ── */
.ds-awards-row{display:flex;gap:8px;flex-wrap:wrap;margin-bottom:14px}
.ds-award-pill{background:#fff8f0;border:1px solid #fcd9b0;color:#8b4000;font-size:0.72rem;font-weight:700;padding:5px 12px;border-radius:99px}
.ds-proof-badge{display:inline-flex;align-items:center;gap:8px;background:#fff8f0;border:1px solid #fcd9b0;color:#8b4000;font-size:0.78rem;font-weight:600;padding:6px 14px;border-radius:99px;margin-bottom:14px}
.ds-pulse{width:8px;height:8px;border-radius:50%;background:#e85d04;animation:ds-pulse 1.5s ease-in-out infinite;flex-shrink:0}
@keyframes ds-pulse{0%,100%{transform:scale(1);opacity:1}50%{transform:scale(1.4);opacity:0.7}}
.ds-stars-row{display:flex;align-items:center;gap:8px;margin-bottom:10px}
.ds-stars{color:#f5a623;font-size:1.1rem;letter-spacing:2px}
.ds-review-ct{font-size:0.78rem;color:#777}
.ds-title{font-size:clamp(1.4rem,3vw,1.95rem);font-weight:900;color:#111;margin:0 0 12px;line-height:1.2;letter-spacing:-0.02em}
.ds-tagline{font-size:0.95rem;color:#555;margin-bottom:18px;line-height:1.6}
.ds-tagline em{color:#e85d04;font-style:normal;font-weight:700}
.ds-price-row{display:flex;align-items:center;gap:10px;flex-wrap:wrap;margin-bottom:6px}
.ds-price{font-size:1.9rem;font-weight:900;color:#111}
.ds-compare{font-size:1.1rem;color:#aaa;text-decoration:line-through}
.ds-save-badge{background:#e85d04;color:#fff;font-size:0.68rem;font-weight:800;letter-spacing:0.05em;padding:4px 10px;border-radius:99px}
.ds-installment{font-size:0.8rem;color:#777;margin-bottom:20px}
.ds-bullets{list-style:none;padding:0;margin:0 0 18px;display:flex;flex-direction:column;gap:8px}
.ds-bullets li{font-size:0.9rem;color:#333;display:flex;align-items:flex-start;gap:8px;line-height:1.45}
.ds-bi{font-size:1rem;flex-shrink:0}
.ds-trust-row{display:flex;gap:6px 16px;flex-wrap:wrap;margin-bottom:18px}
.ds-trust-item{display:flex;align-items:center;gap:5px;font-size:0.78rem;color:#111;font-weight:600}
.ds-trust-item svg{color:#e85d04}
.ds-cta-btn{display:flex;align-items:center;justify-content:center;gap:10px;width:100%;padding:18px 24px;border:none;border-radius:12px;background:linear-gradient(135deg,#bf4500 0%,#e85d04 100%);color:#fff;font-size:1.05rem;font-weight:800;cursor:pointer;letter-spacing:0.01em;box-shadow:0 4px 16px rgba(232,93,4,0.35);transition:transform 0.15s,box-shadow 0.15s}
.ds-cta-btn:hover:not(:disabled){transform:translateY(-2px);box-shadow:0 6px 24px rgba(232,93,4,0.45)}
.ds-cta-btn:disabled{opacity:0.6;cursor:not-allowed}
.ds-ship-note{font-size:0.8rem;color:#666;text-align:center;margin:10px 0 14px}
.ds-ship-note strong{color:#111}
.ds-urgency{display:flex;align-items:center;gap:8px;background:#fff8f0;border:1px solid #fcd9b0;border-radius:10px;padding:10px 16px;font-size:0.8rem;color:#8b4000;margin-bottom:20px}
.ds-urgency svg{color:#e85d04;flex-shrink:0}
.ds-urgency strong{color:#c0392b}
.ds-collapsibles{border-top:1px solid #e8e8e8}
.ds-detail{border-bottom:1px solid #e8e8e8}
.ds-det-sum{display:flex;align-items:center;gap:10px;padding:14px 0;cursor:pointer;font-size:0.9rem;font-weight:700;color:#111;list-style:none;user-select:none}
.ds-det-sum::-webkit-details-marker{display:none}
.ds-chev{margin-left:auto;transition:transform 0.2s;color:#888}
.ds-detail[open] .ds-chev{transform:rotate(180deg)}
.ds-det-body{padding:0 0 14px 28px}
.ds-det-body p{font-size:0.86rem;color:#555;line-height:1.7}

/* ── Video section ── */
.ds-video-section{padding:72px 20px;background:#111}
.ds-video-inner{max-width:960px;margin:0 auto}
.ds-video-section .ds-eyebrow{color:#e85d04}
.ds-video-section .ds-section-title{margin-bottom:32px}
.ds-videos-grid{display:grid;grid-template-columns:repeat(auto-fit,minmax(280px,1fr));gap:20px}
.ds-video-wrap{border-radius:16px;overflow:hidden;background:#000;box-shadow:0 8px 40px rgba(0,0,0,0.5)}
.ds-video-wrap video,.ds-video-wrap iframe{display:block;width:100%;height:auto;max-height:75vh;border:none;object-fit:contain}
.ds-video-wrap iframe{aspect-ratio:16/9;height:auto}

/* ── Ticker ── */
.ds-ticker-strip{background:#111;color:rgba(255,255,255,0.8);padding:12px 0;overflow:hidden;white-space:nowrap}
.ds-ticker-track{display:inline-flex;gap:28px;align-items:center;animation:ds-ticker 40s linear infinite;font-size:0.8rem}
.ds-tsep{color:#e85d04;font-size:0.7rem}
@keyframes ds-ticker{0%{transform:translateX(0)}100%{transform:translateX(-50%)}}

/* ── VS Section ── */
.ds-vs-section{padding:72px 20px;background:#111;color:#fff}
.ds-vs-section .ds-eyebrow{color:#e85d04}
.ds-vs-section .ds-section-title{color:#fff;margin-bottom:48px}
.ds-vs-grid{display:grid;grid-template-columns:1fr 1fr;gap:24px;max-width:860px;margin:0 auto}
@media(max-width:640px){.ds-vs-grid{grid-template-columns:1fr}}
.ds-vs-card{border-radius:20px;overflow:hidden;border:1px solid rgba(255,255,255,0.1)}
.ds-vs-us{border-color:#e85d04;box-shadow:0 0 0 2px #e85d04}
.ds-vs-header{padding:14px 24px;font-size:0.85rem;font-weight:800;letter-spacing:0.08em;text-transform:uppercase;background:#e85d04;color:#fff;text-align:center}
.ds-vs-header--them{background:#2a2a2a;color:rgba(255,255,255,0.5)}
.ds-vs-list{list-style:none;padding:20px 24px;display:flex;flex-direction:column;gap:10px;background:#1a1a1a}
.ds-vs-win{font-size:0.88rem;color:#fff;font-weight:500}
.ds-vs-lose{font-size:0.88rem;color:rgba(255,255,255,0.4)}

/* ── Section shared ── */
.ds-section-inner{max-width:1080px;margin:0 auto}
.ds-eyebrow{font-size:0.68rem;font-weight:800;letter-spacing:0.14em;color:#e85d04;text-transform:uppercase;margin-bottom:8px}
.ds-section-title{font-size:clamp(1.6rem,4vw,2.4rem);font-weight:900;color:#111;letter-spacing:-0.03em;margin-bottom:40px;line-height:1.15}

/* ── Features ── */
.ds-features{padding:72px 20px;background:#fff}
.ds-features-grid{display:grid;grid-template-columns:repeat(2,1fr);gap:28px}
@media(max-width:640px){.ds-features-grid{grid-template-columns:1fr}}
.ds-feat-card{border-radius:16px;overflow:hidden;border:1px solid #eee;background:#f8f8f6}
.ds-feat-img{width:100%;aspect-ratio:4/3;object-fit:cover}
.ds-feat-content{padding:20px}
.ds-feat-content h3{font-size:1rem;font-weight:800;color:#111;margin-bottom:8px}
.ds-feat-content p{font-size:0.86rem;color:#666;line-height:1.65}

/* ── How it works ── */
.ds-how{padding:72px 20px;background:#f8f8f6}
.ds-steps{display:grid;grid-template-columns:repeat(3,1fr);gap:40px;counter-reset:step}
@media(max-width:640px){.ds-steps{grid-template-columns:1fr}}
.ds-step{text-align:center;padding:32px 24px;background:#fff;border-radius:20px;border:1px solid #eee;box-shadow:0 2px 12px rgba(0,0,0,0.04)}
.ds-step-num{font-size:2.5rem;font-weight:900;color:#ffe0cc;margin-bottom:12px;line-height:1}
.ds-step-title{font-size:1.05rem;font-weight:800;color:#111;margin-bottom:10px}
.ds-step-desc{font-size:0.88rem;color:#666;line-height:1.65}

/* ── Reviews ── */
.ds-reviews{padding:72px 20px;background:#fff}
.ds-reviews-grid{display:grid;grid-template-columns:repeat(2,1fr);gap:24px}
@media(max-width:640px){.ds-reviews-grid{grid-template-columns:1fr}}
.ds-review-card{background:#f8f8f6;border-radius:16px;padding:28px 24px;border:1px solid #eee}
.ds-rev-stars{color:#f5a623;font-size:1.1rem;letter-spacing:2px;margin-bottom:14px}
.ds-rev-text{font-size:0.9rem;color:#333;line-height:1.7;margin-bottom:20px;font-style:italic}
.ds-reviewer{display:flex;align-items:center;gap:12px}
.ds-rev-av{width:40px;height:40px;border-radius:50%;background:linear-gradient(135deg,#bf4500,#e85d04);color:#fff;font-weight:800;font-size:1rem;display:flex;align-items:center;justify-content:center;flex-shrink:0}
.ds-reviewer strong{display:block;font-size:0.88rem;color:#111}
.ds-reviewer span{font-size:0.75rem;color:#888}

/* ── FAQ ── */
.ds-faq{padding:72px 20px;background:#f8f8f6}
.ds-faq-inner{max-width:720px;margin:0 auto}
.ds-faq-list{display:flex;flex-direction:column;gap:0}
.ds-faq-item{border:1px solid #e0e0e0;border-radius:12px;margin-bottom:10px;overflow:hidden;background:#fff}
.ds-faq-item[open]{background:#fff8f0}
.ds-faq-q{display:flex;align-items:center;gap:10px;padding:18px 20px;cursor:pointer;font-size:0.93rem;font-weight:700;color:#111;list-style:none;user-select:none}
.ds-faq-q::-webkit-details-marker{display:none}
.ds-faq-q svg{margin-left:auto;transition:transform 0.2s}
.ds-faq-item[open] .ds-faq-q svg{transform:rotate(180deg)}
.ds-faq-a{padding:0 20px 18px 50px;font-size:0.88rem;color:#555;line-height:1.7;margin:0}

/* ── Footer ── */
.ds-footer{background:#111;color:rgba(255,255,255,0.7);padding:56px 24px 24px}
.ds-footer-inner{max-width:1080px;margin:0 auto;display:grid;grid-template-columns:2fr 1fr 1fr;gap:40px;margin-bottom:40px}
@media(max-width:640px){.ds-footer-inner{grid-template-columns:1fr;gap:32px}}
.ds-footer-brand{font-size:1.4rem;font-weight:900;color:#fff;letter-spacing:-0.02em;margin-bottom:8px}
.ds-footer-tagline{font-size:0.85rem;color:rgba(255,255,255,0.45)}
.ds-footer-links{display:flex;flex-direction:column;gap:0}
.ds-footer-links strong{font-size:0.78rem;font-weight:700;color:#e85d04;text-transform:uppercase;letter-spacing:0.08em;margin-bottom:12px}
.ds-footer-links a{font-size:0.85rem;color:rgba(255,255,255,0.55);padding:4px 0;transition:color 0.15s}
.ds-footer-links a:hover{color:#e85d04}
.ds-footer-bottom{max-width:1080px;margin:0 auto;border-top:1px solid rgba(255,255,255,0.08);padding-top:20px;display:flex;align-items:center;justify-content:space-between;flex-wrap:wrap;gap:12px}
.ds-footer-bottom p{font-size:0.78rem;color:rgba(255,255,255,0.35)}
.ds-footer-badges{display:flex;gap:16px;font-size:0.75rem;color:rgba(255,255,255,0.45)}

/* ── Sticky bar ── */
.ds-sticky{position:fixed;bottom:0;left:0;right:0;z-index:500;background:#fff;border-top:1px solid #e0e0e0;padding:12px 20px;display:flex;align-items:center;gap:16px;box-shadow:0 -4px 16px rgba(0,0,0,0.1);transform:translateY(100%);transition:transform 0.3s ease}
.ds-sticky-info{flex:1}
.ds-sticky-info strong{font-size:0.85rem;color:#111;display:block;white-space:nowrap;overflow:hidden;text-overflow:ellipsis;max-width:200px}
.ds-sticky-info span{font-size:1rem;font-weight:800;color:#e85d04}
.ds-sticky-cta{background:linear-gradient(135deg,#bf4500,#e85d04);color:#fff;border:none;border-radius:10px;padding:12px 24px;font-size:0.9rem;font-weight:800;cursor:pointer;white-space:nowrap;flex-shrink:0}
@media(min-width:780px){.ds-sticky{display:none}}
</style>

